title: Renovated 2 Bed + Office In Coolidge Corner - Modern Kitchen and Bath!
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 302926517', 'Rent: $3,200 / Month', 'Beds: 2', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 09/01/2022', 'Pet: Cats Only', 'Rent Includes:: Heat, Hot Water', 'Parking:: off-street parking', 'Very nice apartment that was totally renovated less than a year ago.', ' There are 2 good sized bedrooms, an office, and a renovated kitchen and modern bathroom.', '  It gets great light.', ' There are nice hardwood floors throughout.', ' Heat and hot water are included with the rent.', ' The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher.', ' There is a shared back porch to hang out on.', 'There is laundry in the building.', '  Cats are ok.', " Owner requires 1st month's rent, last month's rent, and a $350 cleaning deposit.", " There is also a 1 month's broker fee.", ' Unit is available 9/1, 9/15, or 10/1.', ' Parking spots are available at $200 per month.', ' Please come take a look soon before this place gets rented.', ' Thanks!', 'Brownstone - Brick', 'Thanks,', 'Steve', 'Steve Sapontzis', '617-590-6508(c)', 'Uptown Realty']
